1.0.16 - Raffael Sahli <sahli@gyselroth.com>
Tue Sept 28 14:35:32 CEST 2017
--
API: [FIX] POST /node/move cannot move a node into a shared mailbox collection which holds a node with the same name #75 
API: [FIX] PUT /file returns Exception\Conflict with code 19 instead of Exception\Forbidden code 40 if a file gets uploaded into a shared mailbox collection and the collection already holds a node with the same name #75
API: [FIX] PUT /file and POST /collection now create a node within a writeonly collection without an Exception\Forbidden response, this feature (writeonly) is deprecated now and will get removed in v2, replacement is the newly (v1.x) introduced permission mailbox)
API: [FIX] PUT /file does not throw an error anymore if an application/zip file with an unknown mimetype gets uploaded


